### Welcome to iCagenda GitHub Page.
There you will be able to edit the language files, and send me directly the info:

```
$ note
$ note2
$ note3
```

### 10 translation packs - 28 sept 2012
Now, we have 10 languages available for iCagenda.

### Authors and Contributors
Owner of the project: @JoomliC.

Translators: Bong (cs-CZ), Roland John van Wanrooy (nl-NL), Lyr!C (en-GB & fr-FR), BMB (de-DE), Giusebos (it-IT), Rikard TÃ¸mte Reitan (nb-NO), Corasouza (pt-BR), MSV (ru-RU), elerizo (es-ES)

Please contact @JoomliC Translation Coordination 

### Support or Contact
